└── docs/             # Put your source documents here
```

## Configuration

Edit `.env` to configure:

| Variable | Description | Default |
|----------|-------------|---------|
| `LLM_PROVIDER` | LLM provider (openai/ollama) | `{{ llm_provider }}` |
| `LLM_MODEL` | Model name | `{{ llm_model }}` |
| `LLM_API_KEY` | API key | - |
| `EMBEDDER_PROVIDER` | Embedding provider | `{{ embedder_provider }}` |
| `EMBEDDER_MODEL` | Embedding model | `{{ embedder_model }}` |
| `VECTORSTORE_TYPE` | Vector DB (chroma/faiss) | `{{ vectorstore_type }}` |
| `TOP_K` | Results to retrieve | `5` |

## Adding Documents

1. Place files in `./docs/` (supports PDF, MD, TXT, DOCX, HTML)
2. Run `python index_docs.py`
3. Start chatting!

## Using Ollama (Local LLM)

```env
LLM_PROVIDER=ollama
LLM_MODEL=llama3
LLM_BASE_URL=http://localhost:11434/v1
```
